title: Ep. 2884 - Chachaji's Arrival - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 16 December 2019
shortDesc: Chachaji gets back to Gokuldham. Jethalal bursts into tears, and everyone happily greets Chachaji on his homecoming. Surprisingly the police get Sakharam on the same day as well. All the tension is now gone. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2885 - Sakharam Is Missing Again - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 17 December 2019
shortDesc: Champak chacha is back home and the best part is that he gets his specs ready to use. Another good news is that Sakharam is found but without its tires. Bhide is a little upset and still gets to bed. Next morning, Sakharam is missing from its spot.

title: Ep. 2886 - Tapu Sena Fix Sakharam - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 18 December 2019
shortDesc: Bhide is tensed about losing Sakharam yet again and then he is also afraid to file a complaint. Later a mechanic comes to the society with Sakharam and Sakharam has its tyres fixed. Tapu Sena tells everyone that they want Sakharam to get fixed.

title: Ep. 2887 - Jethalal Cooks For Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 19 December 2019
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta is sad because of eating the same food every day and to his rescue Jethalal offers him to come to his house for lunch. Jethalal then realizes there is no food for his family members only which makes him cook for everyone. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2888 - Jetha Tries To Cook - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 20 December 2019
shortDesc: Jetha tries to cook a good meal for Goli, Taarak, Chachaji and Tapu. He mixes whatever he finds in the kitchen. When he presents the food it smells great but the taste is awful. He tastes it himself and realizes that he has messed up. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2889 - Iyer's New Boss - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 23 December 2019
shortDesc: Iyer meets his new boss and finds out that they have a lot in common. Iyer invites his boss and his wife for dinner. The problem that arises is that Iyer's boss wants to eat Gujarati food. Iyer wants help from someone to help him and Babita to cook .

title: Ep. 2890 - Jetha's Helping Hand For Iyer - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 24 December 2019
shortDesc: Iyer and Babita reach Taarak's house and asks for help they needed to cook Gujurati dish. Meanwhile, Jethalal arrives and agrees to them that he will cook Gujarati dish for Iyer's boss. Taarak Mehta reminds about his cooking skills, Jethalal agree.

title: Ep. 2891 - Iyer's Bad Day - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 25 December 2019
shortDesc: Iyer and Babita try to contact Jethalal to cook the dinner for their guests as promised but Jethalal goes missing. Iyer gets upset and even his Boss arrives. Iyer's Boss gets really angry upon not getting the desired food and fires Iyer from the job.

title: Ep. 2892 - Baga's Fantastic Idea - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 26 December 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal is upset about what and how to cook at Iyer's house for dinner. Looking at him upset, Baga gives him a fantastic idea that Jethalal should take prepared food to Iyer's house.  And he could say that due to less time he had to do it.

title: Ep. 2893 - Jethalal Is In A Tough Spot - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 27 December 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal tries to seek help from Taarak but fails. Later he starts to make the dinner on his own with the help of Baga and Nattu Kaka. Jethalal is busy with this when an important business contact wants to meet him. He is in a tough spot.

title: Ep. 2894 - Dinner At Iyer's - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 30 December 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal arrives at Iyer's house with prepared food. Iyer's boss calls before they arrive and Iyer speaks of the dish that Jethalal made. His boss tells him to make something else as they are tired of the food that has been prepared.

title: Ep. 2895 - Memories Of The Year Gone By - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 31 December 2019
shortDesc: The people of Gokuldham society come together to celebrate the new year. They want to share and remember the memories that have gone by in this eventful year. Everyone is dressed well and they come to the party for the new year's eve. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2896 - New Year Party - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 1 January 2020
shortDesc: The new party continues at Gokuldham society. They play the music game and share their memories of the bygone year. The entire society enjoys the night together and welcomes the new year. They also dance to the welcoming of the year 2020. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2897 - A New Beginning - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 2 January 2020
shortDesc: Everyone is busy with the new year wishes and Champaklal blesses Jethalal for the new year. Taarak and Anjali also have a great way to start the year and Taarak has an innovative thought for the beginning of the year. Madhvi plays a prank on Bhide.

title: Ep. 2898 - Bhide And Popatlal's Special Guest - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 3 January 2020
shortDesc: Bhide and Popatlal invite a Special guest for the get-together. They invite all the families from Gokuldham society. And all the people get curious about the special guest and starts the preparation. Stay tuned!
